msgid ""
"A library of meshes. Contains a list of :ref:`Mesh <class_Mesh>` "
"resources, each with a name and ID. Each item can also include collision "
"and navigation shapes. This resource is used in :ref:`GridMap "
"<class_GridMap>`."
